The new fragrance with a purpose.

#PoloEarth is the new Polo for all genders and generations to come. Made with 97% natural-origin ingredients from local communities around the world, it is a true exploration of nature.

Discover the collection via the link in bio.

Learn more about Natural Origin ingredients on our product packaging.

#RalphLaurenFragrances

Discover the intensity of #PoloBlue Parfum with @anguscloud. The sophisticated scent draws inspiration from the sea with notes of upcycled oakwood, heightened by mandarin and clary sage, patchouli heart, and smoky vetiver.

#RalphLaurenFragrances

Uplift your senses. #PoloBlue Parfum is an indulgent, yet fresh scent inspired by the freedom of exploring the open seas.

#RalphLaurenFragrances

Sustainability is a journey.

Watch as @lilyachty gives his perspective on sustainability in light of #PoloEarth, the latest step in our ongoing mission to create consciously designed and socially impactful fragrances. This is just the beginning.

Dive deeper into our commitment to sustainability via the link in bio.

#RalphLaurenFragrances

A new generation of fragrance. 

Introducing, #PoloEarth. An indulgent blend of 97% natural-origin ingredients, each finely crafted into a fragrance for all genders. To celebrate the launch of Polo Earth, #RalphLaurenFragrances is partnering with the @arbordayfoundation to plant trees around the world.

Learn more about Natural Origin ingredients on our product packaging.

#PoloBlue parfum is a dynamic blend of upcycled oakwood, sparkling mandarin and clary sage, earthy patchouli, and smoky vetiver. The result is an enveloping, yet rich and seductive scent.
